The paper deals with iris recognition using deep representations, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the impact of preprocessing techniques on iris recognition, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and computer security and cryptography (cs.CR). Finally, the paper specifically focuses on iris recognition in unconstrained environments, which is a subfield of biometrics (cs.IR).
